WHO   — Nynaeve al'Meara — the Wisdom who broke the limits of Healing
WHAT  — Once Wisdom of Emond's Field, one of the strongest channelers in millennia.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: The Yellow Ajah — the art of Healing  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
